    <item>
      <title>南非四党考虑合作治理夸祖鲁-纳塔尔省</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/south-african-elections-four-party-tie-up-planned-in-kwazulu-natal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非民族自由党宣布，已同意与三个较大的竞争对手合作，在东部夸祖鲁-纳塔尔省组建政府，这一协议将有效阻止前总统雅各布·祖马领导的新政党参与，该党在上个月的选举中赢得了该地区最多的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/south-african-elections-four-party-tie-up-planned-in-kwazulu-natal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 16:16:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
